1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All sorrows between you and me.

2
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:35,000
I wonder if that person will come tonight.

3
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,650
Is Fang Ji really trustworthy?

4
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,120
He has studied under Imperial Preceptor Qin since childhood,

5
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,759
and is the son of the current Prime Minister.

6
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,360
Back then, Official Su said

7
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,600
that the Witchcraft Case runs deep,

8
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,930
and many nobles in the court are involved.

9
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,800
Given Fang Ji's background,

10
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,130
I have to be suspicious.

11
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,960
I know him well.

12
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,800
He is a man of integrity.

13
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,240
He remains unsullied by the filth around him.

14
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,840
To clear Official Su's name,

15
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,000
I have endured in the officialdom for over a decade

16
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,160
and seen all kinds of people.

17
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,240
He is the one I trust most in the court.

18
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,080
All right.

19
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,840
The Censorate and the Dragon Shadow Guard are at each other's throats.

20
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,840
If we use this case to our advantage,

21
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:21,640
we can help Fang Ji and the Censorate gain the upper hand

22
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,200
and become the dominant power in the court.

23
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,079
Don't worry.

24
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,200
There won't be any problems.

25
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:28,760
Mm-hmm.

26
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,360
Then I can safely entrust Zhaoxue

27
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:33,920
to Fangji.

28
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,320
Who?

29
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,920
Lord Jian.

30
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,200
Sister Song.

31
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,000
Lord Jian.

32
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,480
Sister Song.

33
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,079
Wake up.

34
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:28,800
Lord Jian.

35
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:29,520
Lord Jian.

36
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:34,560
Go.

37
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:35,960
Leave me.

38
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,360
Go.

39
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,600
Leave me.

40
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,120
Go.

41
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,840
Go!

42
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,200
Sister Song, wake up.

43
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:50,760
Sister Song.

44
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,320
Go! The smoke is poisonous.

45
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:53,640
Go! The smoke is poisonous.

46
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,520
I'm taking you with me.

47
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,200
Hurry.

48
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,600
Go.

49
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,720
Trust no one.

50
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,000
Go.

51
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,600
I'll take you all with me.

52
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,610
Zhaoxue.

53
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,280
Zhaoxue.

54
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:24,810
Zhaoxue.

55
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,140
Xue.

56
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,690
Zhaoxue.

57
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,530
Zhaoxue.

58
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:28,420
Wake up.

59
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,530
Zhaoxue.

60
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:32,810
Zhaoxue.

61
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,450
Zhaoxue.

62
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,400
Zhaoxue.

63
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,370
Zhaoxue.

64
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,800
I need you to live.

65
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,120
I swear I will only marry you in this life.

66
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,440
Do you hear me?

67
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,480
Sister.

68
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,000
You're awake.

69
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,840
Yan'er.

70
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,159
How did I get back?

71
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,880
The Young Marquis carried you back to safety.

72
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,240
He was afraid of delaying your treatment.

73
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:04,000
He rushed back overnight to get the Imperial Physician to see you.

74
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,320
The Young Marquis?

75
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,040
Wasn't it Fang Ji who saved me?

76
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,920
Is she awake?

77
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,920
Sister is awake.

78
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,560
It's one thing for you to run out in the middle of the night,

79
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,920
but you didn't even take me with you.

80
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,850
Do you know that if I had been any later, you'd be dead?

81
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,760
Exactly.

82
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,240
You need to rest and recover.

83
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,280
Sister, during the two days you were in a coma,

84
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,280
the Young Marquis was worried sick.

85
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,200
Don't worry. I will personally find out

86
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,680
who is behind this.

87
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,500
Where is Lord Jian?

88
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,770
And Song Qingniang?

89
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,320
How are they?

90
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,640
What drug did you give Fang Ji?

91
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,200
Lord Fang.

92
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,560
Prime Minister,

93
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,570
it was just a common knockout drug.

94
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,080
Because of your knockout drug,

95
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:03,200
Ji'er has been unconscious for two days.

96
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,440
Even Imperial Physician Hu cannot find the cause.

97
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,570
That's impossible.

98
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,040
We used this drug before.

99
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,680
He woke up very quickly.

100
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,840
Uncle, perhaps the Imperial Physician

101
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,680
has never seen drugs from the martial world,

102
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,080
so he doesn't know how to treat it.

103
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,400
I have sent people to find famous doctors.

104
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,660
My cousin will be fine.

105
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,720
I'll go see him.

106
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,200
Hold on.

107
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:27,240
I won't let you see him.

108
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,080
Stop playing dumb.

109
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,480
It is because of you

110
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,360
that Ji'er is still in a coma.

111
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:42,000
You also caused the deaths of Jian Boning and Song Qingniang.

112
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,400
They're dead?

113
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,040
This debt,

114
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,680
I will settle with you later.

115
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,040
Pack your bags immediately.

116
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:53,250
I'm sending men to escort you back to the Capital.

117
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:57,040
Don't get involved in this case anymore.

118
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:57,880
Uncle.

119
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,320
Prime Minister.

120
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:06,000
You insist on sending me back to the Capital now.

121
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:11,040
Is it because you're taking your anger about Fang Ji out on me?

122
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,400
Or is it simply

123
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:16,570
that you don't want me investigating this case any further?

124
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,240
Miss Gu,

125
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,200
what are you implying?

126
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,840
As far as I know,

127
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:29,680
you and Imperial Preceptor Qin have always been close.

128
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:32,480
You were the one who introduced him to the capital.

129
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:35,039
It wasn't until your wife passed away

130
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:37,440
that you two started drifting apart.

131
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,679
The real break in your relationship

132
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,120
happened after the Witchcraft Case.

133
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,520
This is a private matter of the Fang family.

134
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,800
I have no comment.

135
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,680
However,

136
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:53,600
regarding the matter of Jian Boning and Song Qingniang,

137
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,360
hasn't it made you realize, Miss Gu,

138
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,560
that for some things,

139
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,700
the less you know, the better?

140
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,080
I have a flaw.

141
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,080
I am stubborn.

142
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,610
Since clues have surfaced,

143
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,690
I must get to the bottom of this.

144
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,280
My Lord.

145
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,400
Lead the way.

146
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:16,930
Yes, sir.

147
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,600
Come with me.

148
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,650
Rest for a while.

149
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,880
They are dead.

150
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,360
Don't dwell on it.

151
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:34,520
The most important thing now is to recover from your injuries.

152
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,580
I'll be right back.

153
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,280
Fangji.

154
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,200
Is it really you?

155
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,450
Zhaoxue.

156
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:20,690
Zhaoxue.

157
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:21,960
Zhaoxue.

158
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,120
I'm here.

159
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,400
Come in.

160
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,120
Young Marquis.

161
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:50,160
Imperial Physician Hu said you've recovered.

162
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:52,960
Let's go.

163
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,920
Where to?

164
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,920
Prime Minister Fang is taking Fang Ji home to recuperate.

165
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,050
Let's go visit them.

166
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:01,680
He...

167
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,120
How is he?

168
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,880
He won't die. Don't worry.

169
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,520
I've found a master.

170
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,020
He can surely cure him.

171
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:32,960
Uncle, this is Daoist Priest Miaoxu from Shennong Temple in Jinzhou.

172
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,920
He has great powers.

173
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:35,450
He has cured similar cases.

174
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,360
Greetings, Prime Minister.

175
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,760
Daoist Master.

176
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:01,920
It is just as I calculated in the temple.

177
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:05,320
Censor Fang has been afflicted by an evil spirit.

178
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:15,600
If a woman with this horoscope marries him,

179
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:18,400
the joyous energy will dispel the evil spirit.

180
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,840
This...

181
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,720
This is exactly my horoscope.

182
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,650
Your horoscope?

183
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:28,320
Yes.

184
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,280
It is.

185
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,640
Censor Fang is indeed a man of great fortune.

186
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,280
I was worried that

187
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:38,280
finding such a person would be like looking for a needle in a haystack.

188
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:42,480
I didn't expect Censor Fang's destiny to be right before our eyes.

189
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,720
The official wife of the Fang family's legitimate son

190
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,960
cannot be a woman of unknown origin.

191
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,170
This is absolutely unacceptable.

192
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,880
Prime Minister, you need not worry.

193
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,440
As long as she enters the Fang household,

194
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,080
whether as a wife or a concubine,

195
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,160
it will suffice.

196
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:03,410
You just need to hold the ceremony as if taking an official wife.

197
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:07,330
However, I'm afraid this might be unfair to this young lady.

198
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,760
I don't feel wronged.

199
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,480
Yan'er.

200
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:17,160
Sister, you know I've had feelings for Master Fang for a long time.

201
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:18,440
Let alone being a concubine,

202
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,600
even if it cost me my life,

203
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:20,760
I would be willing.

204
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:25,840
Besides, Master Fang woke up once last night.

205
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,480
I...

206
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,080
I'm already his.

207
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,080
She's the one insisting on degrading herself.

208
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,210
Why worry about her?

209
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,280
If you keep feeding them like this,

210
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:06,410
the fish in this pond

211
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,960
are going to go belly up.

212
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:08,940
Go away.

213
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:14,240
Fang Ji's marriage to your sister is settled.

214
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,260
Have you still not gotten over it?

215
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:19,540
They say a grown child is beyond a mother's control,

216
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,880
let alone a sister.

217
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,890
Do you even know how to talk?

218
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,930
If you can't comfort me, save your breath.

219
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,280
I'm sorry.

220
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:32,460
I just don't want to see you so sad.

221
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,160
I'm not.

222
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:41,160
My mind is just a mess.

223
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:42,800
Fang Ji...

224
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,640
My sister...

225
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,770
I can't believe they're together.

226
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,800
Why worry about them?

227
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,440
You have me, anyway.

228
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:57,640
Although I come from a family of officials,

229
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,900
and many things are out of my control,

230
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,480
as long as it's what I want,

231
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,480
no one can stop me.

232
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:06,680
Su Zhaoxue.

233
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,330
Actually, you can trust me,

234
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:11,600
and rely on me.

235
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,080
Actually,

236
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:18,080
I've known for a long time that you are Lord Su Ziliang's daughter.

237
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:21,080
When I saved you from Zhou Laohu's bandit stronghold,

238
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:23,100
I began to suspect your identity,

239
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:27,610
so I had Pihu ask the Longying Guards in the capital to investigate.

240
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:28,840
I'm sorry.

241
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,960
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

242
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:31,440
I just...

243
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,320
I know.

244
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,720
You don't need to explain.

245
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:38,040
I also know the Su family must have been wrongly accused.

246
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:39,680
Zhaoxue,

247
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,320
I care about you.

248
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,360
So rest assured,

249
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,260
I will help you clear your father's name.

250
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:47,660
Young Marquis,

251
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,680
thank you.

252
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,080
But,

253
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:55,960
I should handle this myself.

254
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,280
I won't drag you into it.

255
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:01,680
Zhaoxue,

256
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:05,760
no matter what, I'm here.

257
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:14,200
I will keep waiting.

258
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:23,040
Misty rain, a dream.
